Richard Emory https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Emory 0 Richard Emory (January 27, 1919 – February 15, 1994) was the first-born son of show business parents. He would achieve his fame as an American B-movie actor of the 1950s and 1960s. He would also play supporting roles in various television series of the same period. He retired from movies and television in 1963. Richard_Emory ( January_27_,_1919 – February_15_,_1994 ) was the_first-born_son of show_business_parents .
